073,"uid":121420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:31:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab18c166cd95d13953c75dc606f5e93cc82eba71","tid":1412073,"uid":6073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:34:12.000Z","msg":"居民已成功屌走班狗"},{"pid":"f40a9bdacd33ea95e9c48e4d97628e2f94a53312","tid":1412073,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:40:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd48bbc220982b4576b99eb2a70d18ff4550374e","tid":1412073,"uid":17812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:53:39.000Z","msg":"召喚所有啟勝管理嘅居苑住戶<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kaishing.hk/resident/kaishing/contact_us.do?company=kaishing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kaishing.hk%2Fresident%2Fkaishing%2Fcontact_us.do%3Fcompany%3Dkaishing&d=7QdSi1Eq0NVbLWVUesVCWGXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=b0d4ea61\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kaishing.hk/resident/kaishing/contact_us.do?company=kaishing</a><br />\n<br />\n本人想查詢啟勝對近日示威事件之處理手法。<br />\n昨日天盛苑（同屬啟勝管理）管理員居然肆意讓警察進入屋苑範圍內，更任由警員在內施放催淚彈、妄顧居民安全。<br />\n本人不希望同類事情發生於本屋苑範圍內，希望貴公司能及早計劃對策，妥善處理應否讓警員在沒有搜查令之下進入本苑。"}]}